Distribution
************

   @{b}MUI-FReq@{ub} is distribuited under the concept of ShareWare: if you use
this program, you are required to send 10.000 Lit. or the equivalent of
8 US$ in any currency to the author. This program is not crippled in
any way, however future releases depends heavily on how much feedback
it will have.

   If you can't afford paying money for @{b}MUI-FReq@{ub}, send me at least a
postcard with your comments. For the address, see @{"Author Info" Link "Author Info"}.


@EndNode

